<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1h0004-zh-1312964b" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>論語新注新譯</title><editor role="translator">Yang Fengbin 楊逢彬 2016</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>論語新注新譯</title>北京　北京大學出版社，2016</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR1h0004"><title xml:lang="och">論語</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2023-10-18T18:02:53.125+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2023-10-21T19:23:40.627+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2024-01-25T07:00:28.72+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR1h0004-start"><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:10:42.007+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:10:51.474+09:00">“學了後又定時複習它ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:10:59.897+09:00">不是很高興嗎?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:11:19.314+09:00"> 朋友從遠方來ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:11:33.908+09:00">不是很快樂嗎?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:11:44.976+09:00">别人不瞭解我ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:11:47.969+09:00">我卻不氣惱ꎬ這不就是君子嗎?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:12:21.633+09:00">有子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:13:21.102+09:00">“一個人的爲人ꎬ既孝順父母ꎬ又敬愛兄長ꎬ卻喜歡冒犯上級ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:13:34.521+09:00">這種人是很少的ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:13:46.759+09:00">不喜歡冒犯上級ꎬ卻喜歡造反ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:14:42.324+09:00">這種人從來没有過ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:14:55.336+09:00">君子致力於打基礎ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:15:14.156+09:00">基礎鞏固了ꎬ‘道’就會産生ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:15:56.647+09:00">孝順父母ꎬ敬愛兄長ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:16:29.728+09:00">這就是‘仁’的基礎吧!”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:16:41.311+09:00">【譯文】孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:17:02.702+09:00">“花言巧語ꎬ滿臉堆笑ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:17:10.474+09:00">[這種人ꎬ]是不會有多少‘仁德’的ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:17:37.212+09:00">曾子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:17:49.753+09:00">“我每天多次反省自己:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:17:57.104+09:00">爲别人辦事是否盡心竭力了呢?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:18:07.204+09:00">和朋友交往是否誠實呢?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:18:09.878+09:00">老師傳授給我的學業是否複習了呢?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:18:52.256+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:19:09.595+09:00">“治理具有千輛兵車的國家ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:19:18.382+09:00">辦事要嚴肅認真ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:19:29.749+09:00">誠實無欺ꎬ節約費用ꎬ愛護他人ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:19:55.353+09:00">役使老百姓要在農閒時間ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:02.949+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:11.592+09:00">“後生小子ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:19.145+09:00">在家便孝順父母ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:23.516+09:00">出門便敬愛兄長ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:33.677+09:00">謹慎而且信實ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:43.188+09:00">博愛大衆ꎬ親近有仁德的人ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:20:53.875+09:00">這樣躬行實踐之後ꎬ有剩餘力量ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:21:48.181+09:00">就再去學習文獻ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:23:18.927+09:00">子夏説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:23:32.54+09:00">“尊敬賢者ꎬ輕視美色ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:23:42.302+09:00">侍奉爹娘ꎬ能盡全力ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:23:54.82+09:00">侍奉君上ꎬ能够獻身ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:24:05.798+09:00">和朋友相交ꎬ説話一定誠實守信ꎮ 這種人ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:24:34.188+09:00">即便没有系統學習過ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:24:40.208+09:00">我一定説他已經學過了ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:25:11.729+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:25:20.503+09:00">“君子ꎬ不莊重ꎬ就没有威嚴ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:25:34.292+09:00">學習了ꎬ就不致固陋無知ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:25:40.782+09:00">要時時恪守忠誠信實ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:25:53.855+09:00">不要跟不如自己的人交朋友ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:26:00.093+09:00">有了過錯ꎬ就不要怕改正ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:26:26.236+09:00">曾子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:26:30.766+09:00">“審慎地對待年長者的死亡ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:26:42.296+09:00">追念故去已久的人ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:26:44.595+09:00">老百姓自然會歸於忠厚老實了ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:27:14.753+09:00">子禽問子貢説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:27:22.828+09:00">“他老先生到哪個國家ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:27:49.652+09:00">必然聽到該國的政事ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:27:56.245+09:00">是打聽到的呢?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:28:06.366+09:00">還是别人主動告訴的呢?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:28:12.932+09:00">子貢説:“</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:29:37.204+09:00">他老先生是靠温和、善良、恭敬、節儉、謙讓來獲得的ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:29:40.744+09:00">他老人家獲得的方法ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:29:29.943+09:00">和别人獲得的方法ꎬ大概不同吧?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:07.323+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:14.875+09:00">“他父親還健在ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:23.589+09:00">要觀察他的志向ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:30.664+09:00">父親不在了ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:40.214+09:00">要考察他的行爲ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:56.188+09:00">如果他長期不改變父親的合理做法ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:30:57.268+09:00">就可以説是盡孝了ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:03.616+09:00">有子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:09.767+09:00">“禮的作用ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:16.641+09:00">以和諧爲可貴ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:25.234+09:00">過去聖明君王的治理天下ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:31.371+09:00">以這一點最爲美好ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:38.442+09:00">但是ꎬ小事大事都循此而行ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:45.936+09:00">有些事就不一定能行得通了ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:52.298+09:00">爲了和諧而和諧ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-12a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:58.436+09:00">不用禮儀制度來節制ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:32:58.747+09:00">也是行不通的ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:33:42.251+09:00">有子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:33:51.563+09:00">“諾言大致符合義ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:33:55.955+09:00">説的話就能兑現ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:06.2+09:00">態度容貌端莊而合於禮ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:14.204+09:00">就不會遭受侮辱ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:22.716+09:00">對姻親保持親近ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:23.188+09:00">[這種態度]也是值得推崇的ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:43.462+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:34:52.017+09:00">“君子ꎬ吃飯不追求吃飽ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:35:04.649+09:00">居住不追求安逸ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:35:50.649+09:00">工作勤勞敏捷ꎬ説話卻惜字如金ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:36:11.542+09:00">去得道之人那兒匡正自己ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:36:12.536+09:00">這樣ꎬ可以説是好學了ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:36:54.904+09:00">子貢説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:37:08.483+09:00">“貧窮卻不諂媚ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:37:23.672+09:00">有錢卻不驕泰ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:40:14.121+09:00">怎麽樣?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:39:04.1+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:40:47.418+09:00">“可以了ꎻ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-15a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:40:54.922+09:00">但不如貧窮卻又快樂ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:40:59.428+09:00">有錢卻謙虛好禮呢ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:41:05.802+09:00">子貢説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:41:25.617+09:00">“«詩經»上説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:41:32.584+09:00">‘好比象骨細切磋ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:23.754+09:00">又像玉石細琢磨ꎮ’</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:30.43+09:00">就是這個意思吧?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:38.498+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:46.906+09:00">“賜啊ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-16a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:56.988+09:00">現在可以和你討論«詩經»了ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-17a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:42:57.719+09:00">告訴你已知的ꎬ你能推知未知的了ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:43:23.862+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-17a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:43:32.259+09:00">“我不擔心别人不瞭解我ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-17a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-18T18:43:34.306+09:00">我擔心自己不瞭解别人ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-15T18:26:31.105+09:00">子貢説:“我不希望别人[把侮辱]施加給我，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:01:59.812+09:00">我也不希望[把它]施加給别人。”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:01:32.05+09:00">孔子説:“賜啊，這不是你能做到的。”　【</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:44:10.927+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:44:38.774+09:00">“我没有見過愛好仁德的人</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:45:01.641+09:00">和厭惡不仁的人。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:45:31.136+09:00">愛好仁德的人，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:45:46.701+09:00">那是再好不過的了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:45:58.916+09:00">厭惡不仁德的人，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:46:09.434+09:00">他行仁德</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:46:29.901+09:00">只是不想沾染上不仁德的東西。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:46:46.301+09:00">有誰能在某日致力於仁德呢?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:47:07.391+09:00"> 我没見過力量不够的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:47:30.945+09:00">大概還是有這樣的人ꎬ我没有見到罷了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-16a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:03:42.021+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:02:35.234+09:00">“由!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-17a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:03:58.859+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:04:10.063+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:03:55.992+09:00">“由!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:04:07.464+09:00">教你如何獲取知識變得智慧吧!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:04:20.882+09:00">知道就是知道，不知道就是不知道。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:08:35.757+09:00">這就是聰明智慧。”　</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:25:38.1+09:00">想要歸於純正’ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:25:56.729+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:26:06.104+09:00">“«詩經»三百篇ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:26:17.971+09:00">用一句話來概括它ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:28:11.665+09:00">就是‘</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:31:41.493+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:32:03.613+09:00">“用政令引導他們ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:32:18.026+09:00">用刑罰整頓他們ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:32:28.864+09:00">人民只是免於罪過ꎬ卻没有廉恥之心ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:32:40.539+09:00">若用道德引導他們ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:32:50.683+09:00">用禮教整頓他們ꎬ人民</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T17:33:29.682+09:00">不但有廉恥之心ꎬ而且人心歸服ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-28a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T19:59:06.173+09:00">孔子評價«韶»説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-28a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T20:00:38.602+09:00">“美極了ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-28a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T20:00:49.99+09:00">而且好極了ꎮ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-28a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T20:01:03.665+09:00">”評價«武»説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-28a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T20:01:13.677+09:00">“美極了ꎬ</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_003-29a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-04T20:01:21.11+09:00">卻還不够好ꎮ”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:56:12.487+09:00">仲弓問子桑伯子這人怎樣。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:56:21.45+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:49:01.644+09:00">“這人不錯，簡潔明快.”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:56:47.999+09:00">仲弓説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:48:15.317+09:00">“平素嚴肅認真禮儀周全,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:48:19.62+09:00">行事卻簡潔明快ꎬ這樣來治理百姓,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:57:24.665+09:00">不也挺好嗎?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:48:32.829+09:00">平素隨便散漫ꎬ行事也一味求簡求快,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:58:05.847+09:00">不是有些簡單粗暴了嗎?”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:58:13.785+09:00">孔子説:</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T21:58:17.902+09:00">“你這話説得對!”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:47:09.823+09:00">“孔子説：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-31T22:47:21.311+09:00">“冉雍這個人，有能力君臨天下。”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:44:11.472+09:00">“冉求説：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:44:30.975+09:00">“不是不喜歡您的學説，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:44:40.693+09:00">是力量不够。”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:44:50.709+09:00">孔子説：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:50:15.222+09:00">“力量不够的人，　【“【考證 】力不足者：這四字理解有歧異，一説“者”是一表停頓的語氣詞，有時兼表假設語氣。楊伯峻先生取此説，並云參見其《文言語法》一書。一説指“力量不夠的人”，如同《里仁》第六章之“我未見力不足者”。孫欽善等取此説。根據漢儒的理解，“力不足者”的“者”並非表假設的標記。知者，在注“魯無君子者，斯焉取斯”時，何晏《集解》引包咸説：“如魯無君子，子賤安得此行而學行之？”唐寫本《論語》鄭玄注：“魯若無君子之仁（人），此仁（人）於何取此道而學行之也？”可見依其體例，漢儒根據當時的語感理解“者”爲表假設的標記時，即以“如”“若”注明之。而注此章時，何晏《集解》引孔安國説：“力不足者當中道而廢，今女自止耳，非力極也。”唐寫本《論語》鄭玄注則云：“力疲倦者，當如牛馬之□（原文此处为□）而廢伏；今汝計畫才力，豫止不前。”都未以“如”“若”注出。因此，在未能證明這一“力不足者”與4.6的“力不足者”（“我未見力不足者”）有所區别之前，我們暫取後説。（51）”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-18a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:45:01.181+09:00">會半途而廢；</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_006-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-01T19:45:03.481+09:00">現在你卻還没走就打起了小算盤。”</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>